	<div class="summary entry-summary">
		<h1 class="product_title entry-title">Fast Speed Fabric Printing Machine</h1><p class="price"></p>
<div class="woocommerce-product-details__short-description">
	<h2><span data-preserver-spaces="true">key feature</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">Dual ink system for both direct-to-fabric (DTF) and dye-sublimation printing</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">Wide-format printing capability up to 1800 mm</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">High-resolution output up to 1200 dpi for detailed and vibrant prints</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">Industrial-grade printing speed: hundreds of square meters per hour</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">Advanced digital control system for precise image registration and stability</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">Multi-color printing support for complex patterns and full-color designs</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">Compatible with cotton, silk, polyester, nylon, and other textile materials</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">User-friendly interface with intuitive controls and workflow</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">Automatic cleaning system for low maintenance and consistent performance</span></li>
<li><span data-preserver-spaces="true">Energy-efficient and eco-friendly design for sustainable production</span></li>
</ul>
